Uses of Interface
org.codehaus.mojo.mrm.api.FileSystem

  • Packages that use FileSystem 
    Package Description
    org.codehaus.mojo.mrm.api
    This is the core contract of a repository.
    org.codehaus.mojo.mrm.plugin
    This is the contract for the Maven Plugin Extensions that allow for plugging in custom repository types into the Maven plugin.
